00:25:05,626 --> 00:25:06,709
Nishimiya,

278
00:25:08,584 --> 00:25:10,167
can we be

279
00:25:11,042 --> 00:25:12,417
friends?

280
00:25:13,792 --> 00:25:15,417
Damn, what am I saying!?

281
00:25:16,459 --> 00:25:19,792
