630
00:47:37,709 --> 00:47:38,417
Hey!

631
00:47:41,209 --> 00:47:43,083
Hi Yuzuru-kun,

632
00:47:43,459 --> 00:47:45,501
Please eat enough!

633
00:47:45,626 --> 00:47:46,626
