660
00:49:44,209 --> 00:49:45,417
I see...

661
00:49:45,584 --> 00:49:47,709
I was said she didn't need me.

662
00:49:49,918 --> 00:49:52,459
Hey, you live together with her!?

663
00:49:55,542 --> 00:49:57,667
