679
00:50:47,584 --> 00:50:49,667
I'm the worst human being.

680
00:50:50,292 --> 00:50:52,918
I'm the one who don't worth living.

681
00:50:53,959 --> 00:50:55,209
But, at least,

682
00:50:56,042 --> 00:50:59,626
