691
00:51:40,459 --> 00:51:41,459
Understood?

692
00:51:49,626 --> 00:51:50,667
You are her little sis!?

693
00:51:50,792 --> 00:51:51,792
Bye!

694
00:51:59,834 --> 00:52:02,834
