699
00:52:22,417 --> 00:52:23,417
Yu-ju,

700
00:52:23,459 --> 00:52:24,834
Hey, sis!

701
00:52:24,959 --> 00:52:26,959
I'b zorry, I'b zorry!

702
00:52:27,334 --> 00:52:29,417
Me too.

703
