718
00:53:13,209 --> 00:53:16,083
I'm glad to see a friend of my best friend Ya-sho.

719
00:53:16,876 --> 00:53:18,083
He is my classmate,

720
00:53:18,209 --> 00:53:20,918
Na-ga-tsu-ka.

